-- Football Player Aaron Hernandez Is Charged With Murder
-- B y   D o n   J e f f r e y
-- 2013-06-26T18:49:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-26/football-player-aaron-hernandez-is-charged-with-murder.html
Aaron Hernandez , a tight end on the
New England Patriots football team, was charged with murder
after being arrested by the police in North Attleboro,
Massachusetts.  Hernandez was arraigned today in district court in
Attleboro, Massachusetts.  To contact the reporter on this story:
